author: Simon Nixon
title: Weekend Tallies Pose Challenge for Europe
text:
The coming weekend will be the most significant moment in European politics since the French presidential election in April, with important votes taking place in two of the European Union’s three biggest countries. The government of the third one, France, will be awaiting the results with particular interest.
